    <description><![CDATA[<h2 id="安装-meld-如果缺少的话">安装 meld (如果缺少的话)</h2>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-Shell">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-Shell" data-lang="Shell"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nb">cd</span> /usr/local
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">wget https://pypi.python.org/packages/0f/5e/3a57c223d8faba2c3c2d69699f7e6cfdd1e5cc31e79cdd0dd48d44580b50/meld3-1.0.1.tar.gz#md5<span class="o">=</span>2f045abe0ae108e3c8343172cffbe21d
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">tar -zxvf meld3-1.0.1.tar.gz
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nb">cd</span> meld3-1.0.1
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">python setup.py install</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h2 id="安装-supervisor3">安装 supervisor3</h2>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-Shell">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-Shell" data-lang="Shell"><span class="line"><span class="cl">wget https://pypi.python.org/packages/source/s/supervisor/supervisor-3.0b2.tar.gz --no-check-certificate
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">tar -zxvf supervisor-3.0b2.tar.gz
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nb">cd</span> supervisor-3.0b2
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">python setup.py install
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">yum install python-setuptools</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h2 id="创建日志文件">创建日志文件</h2>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-Shell">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-Shell" data-lang="Shell"><span class="line"><span class="cl">touch /var/log/supervisord.log
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">chmod <span class="m">755</span> /var/log/supervisord.log</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h2 id="创建默认的配置文件">创建默认的配置文件</h2>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-Shell">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-Shell" data-lang="Shell"><span class="line"><span class="cl">echo_supervisord_conf &gt; /etc/supervisord.conf</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h2 id="修改etcsupervisordconf">修改/etc/supervisord.conf</h2>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl"># 添加到末尾
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">[include]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">files = /etc/supervisord.d/\*.ini</span></span></code></pre></div></div>]]></description>
